sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_8e319f312f273010c742b8e72799b6d2
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>cmdb_ci_database</collection><condition>current.db_server.changes()</condition><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>[Tidal] Update Server Relationship</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    if (current.db_server.getDisplayValue() != '') {
        addRelationship(current.sys_id, current.db_server.sys_id);
    }
    removeRelationship(current.sys_id, previous.db_server.sys_id);

    function removeRelationship(db, server) {
        var rel = new GlideRecord('cmdb_rel_ci');
        rel.addQuery('parent', db);
        rel.addQuery('child', server);
        rel.query();
        while (rel.next()) {
            rel.deleteRecord();
        }
    }

    function addRelationship(db, server) {
        var rel = new GlideRecord('cmdb_rel_ci');
        rel.initialize();
        rel.parent = db;
        rel.child = server;
        rel.type.setDisplayValue('Runs on::Runs');
        rel.insert();
    }

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-11-02 01:04:18</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>8e319f312f273010c742b8e72799b6d2</sys_id><sys_mod_count>11</sys_mod_count><sys_name>[Tidal] Update Server Relationship</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Tidal CI Integration" source="x_74235_tidal_ci">323bb3022f3ed4101fb2e93df699b66c</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Tidal CI Integration">323bb3022f3ed4101fb2e93df699b66c</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_8e319f312f273010c742b8e72799b6d2</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-12-10 15:52:11</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=8e319f312f273010c742b8e72799b6d2"/></record_update>

    if (source.action == 'remove') {
